">AI Factory</a>, Autumn 2005</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jeff Rollason</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aifactory.co.uk/newsletter/2006_01_fuzzy_books.htm\">Fuzzy books - Approximate opening knowledge</a></i>. <a href=\"/AI_Factory\" title=\"AI Factory\">AI Factory</a>, Spring 2006&#160;» <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jeff Rollason</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aifactory.co.uk/newsletter/2006_03_quiescence_alts.htm\">Looking for Alternatives to Quiescence Search</a></i>. <a href=\"/AI_Factory\" title=\"AI Factory\">AI Factory</a>, Autumn 2006&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a>, <a href=\"/SOMA\" title=\"SOMA\">SOMA</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jeff Rollason</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aifactory.co.uk/newsletter/2005_04_stronger-by-learning.htm\">Playing Stronger by learning</a></i>. <a href=\"/AI_Factory\" title=\"AI Factory\">AI Factory</a>, Winter 2006&#160;» <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">Learning</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jeff Rollason</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aifactory.co.uk/newsletter/2005_04_plausibility_analysis.htm\">Driving search with Plausibility analysis: Looking at the right moves</a></i>. <a href=\"/AI_Factory\" title=\"AI Factory\">AI Factory</a>, Winter 2006&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jeff Rollason</a> (<b>2007</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aifactory.co.uk/newsletter/2007_01_neg_plausibility.htm\">Negative Plausibility</a></i>. <a href=\"/AI_Factory\" title=\"AI Factory\">AI Factory</a>, Spring 2007&